				<header class="page-header">
					<h1>Start Playing Untamed</h1>
					<p class="subtitle">Your first hunt begins here</p>
				</header>

				<article class="content">
					<div class="intro-banner">
						<p>This guide will get you from zero to your first hunt in under 30 minutes. Let's hunt.</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Section 1: What You Need -->
					<section class="guide-section">
						<div class="section-number">1</div>
						<h2>What You Need</h2>

						<div class="checklist-grid">
							<div class="checklist-card required">
								<h3>‚úÖ Required</h3>
								<ul>
									<li>1 GM</li>
									<li>At least 2 Hunters</li>
									<li>A dice set (d20, d6, d4)</li>
									<li>Character Sheet</li>
									<li>One Monster Stat Block</li>
									<li>A Biome</li>
								</ul>
							</div>

							<div class="checklist-card optional">
								<h3>üìã Optional (Recommended)</h3>
								<ul>
									<li><a href="/quick-reference">Quick Reference page</a> (keep it open)</li>
									<li>Sector map sketch</li>
									<li>Miniatures or tokens</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 2: Create Your Hunter -->
					<section class="guide-section">
						<div class="section-number">2</div>
						<h2>Create Your Hunter</h2>
						<p class="section-subtitle">Quick Version</p>

						<div class="info-box">
							<p>üìñ <strong>Full details:</strong> See <a href="/character">Character Creation page</a> for complete rules.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="step-list">
							<div class="step-card">
								<div class="step-header">
									<span class="step-num">Step 1</span>
									<h3>Choose a Race</h3>
								</div>
								<p>Pick your race. Gain:</p>
								<ul>
									<li>Stat bonus</li>
									<li>Proficiencies</li>
									<li>Racial trait</li>
								</ul>
							</div>

							<div class="step-card">
								<div class="step-header">
									<span class="step-num">Step 2</span>
									<h3>Choose a Background</h3>
								</div>
								<p>Gain:</p>
								<ul>
									<li>+2 / +1 stats</li>
									<li>3 proficiencies</li>
									<li>1 trait</li>
									<li>1 tool proficiency</li>
								</ul>
								<p><strong>Then choose 1 common tool proficiency</strong></p>
							</div>

							<div class="step-card">
								<div class="step-header">
									<span class="step-num">Step 3</span>
									<h3>Assign Stats</h3>
								</div>
								<p>Distribute starting stat points based on your system.</p>
							</div>

							<div class="step-card">
								<div class="step-header">
									<span class="step-num">Step 4</span>
									<h3>Choose a Weapon</h3>
								</div>
								<p>Start <strong>Trained (+2)</strong> in one weapon.</p>
								<p>Others begin <strong>Novice (+0)</strong>.</p>
							</div>

							<div class="step-card">
								<div class="step-header">
									<span class="step-num">Step 5</span>
									<h3>Calculate</h3>
								</div>
								<div class="formula-list">
									<div class="formula">HP = (CON √ó 6) + Hunter Rank</div>
									<div class="formula">Stamina = 6 + CON mod</div>
									<div class="formula">AR = 10 + armor</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 3: Form a Hunting Party -->
					<section class="guide-section">
						<div class="section-number">3</div>
						<h2>Form a Hunting Party</h2>

						<p>Hunters should coordinate roles:</p>

						<div class="role-grid">
							<div class="role-card frontline">
								<h3>üõ° Frontliner</h3>
								<p>Block / Parry</p>
								<p class="role-desc">Absorbs attacks, protects the party</p>
							</div>

							<div class="role-card damage">
								<h3>‚öîÔ∏è Damage Dealer</h3>
								<p>High attack output</p>
								<p class="role-desc">Focuses on breaking parts and dealing damage</p>
							</div>

							<div class="role-card control">
								<h3>üéØ Control</h3>
								<p>Traps / Study Target</p>
								<p class="role-desc">Sets up advantages, analyzes weaknesses</p>
							</div>

							<div class="role-card support">
								<h3>üéµ Support</h3>
								<p>Flute / Guarded Stance / Cooking</p>
								<p class="role-desc">Buffs party, manages resources</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="callout-box">
							<p><strong>Untamed rewards coordination.</strong><br>Part breaks are easier together.</p>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 4: Choose a Hunt -->
					<section class="guide-section">
						<div class="section-number">4</div>
						<h2>Choose a Hunt</h2>

						<p>GM selects:</p>
						<ul class="hunt-checklist">
							<li>A biome</li>
							<li>A Tier-appropriate monster</li>
							<li>A sector map (loose sketch)</li>
						</ul>

						<div class="warning-banner">
							<p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è At HR 0‚Äì4:</strong> Use Tier 1 monsters only.</p>
						</div>

						<h3>The 3 Hunt Types</h3>

						<div class="hunt-types">
							<div class="hunt-type-card">
								<h4>üéØ Standard Hunt</h4>
								<p>Kill or repel the monster</p>
							</div>

							<div class="hunt-type-card">
								<h4>üì¶ Objective Hunt</h4>
								<p>Rescue / escort / recover</p>
							</div>

							<div class="hunt-type-card">
								<h4>üîç Investigation Hunt</h4>
								<p>Track & learn about the monster</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 5: Run Your First Hunt -->
					<section class="guide-section">
						<div class="section-number">5</div>
						<h2>Run Your First Hunt</h2>
						<p class="section-subtitle">Mini Script</p>

						<p>Here's what a sample turn looks like:</p>

						<div class="example-script">
							<div class="script-line gm">
								<span class="speaker">GM:</span>
								<span class="dialogue">"The Vorvarg snarls and charges toward you through the mist."</span>
							</div>

							<div class="script-action">
								<strong>‚Üí Roll Initiative</strong> (d20 + DEX)
							</div>

							<div class="script-line player">
								<span class="speaker">Hunter A:</span>
								<span class="dialogue">"I move forward and attack with my greatsword!"</span>
							</div>

							<div class="script-action">
								<strong>‚Üí Rolls attack, spends 1 Stamina</strong>
							</div>

							<div class="script-line player">
								<span class="speaker">Hunter B:</span>
								<span class="dialogue">"I use Steady Aim, focusing on its weak point."</span>
							</div>

							<div class="script-action">
								<strong>‚Üí Uses Preparation Action, gains +2 Stamina at end of turn</strong>
							</div>

							<div class="script-line gm">
								<span class="speaker">GM:</span>
								<span class="dialogue">"The Vorvarg bites at Hunter A!"</span>
							</div>

							<div class="script-line player">
								<span class="speaker">Hunter A:</span>
								<span class="dialogue">"I Block!"</span>
							</div>

							<div class="script-action">
								<strong>‚Üí Spends 1 Stamina, gains +3 AR vs the attack</strong>
							</div>

							<div class="script-action">
								<strong>‚Üí End of round: Resolve stamina recovery</strong>
								<ul>
									<li>Hunter A used Action + Fast Action ‚Üí No recovery</li>
									<li>Hunter B used Preparation ‚Üí Gains +2 Stamina</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="tip-box">
							<h4>üí° Tips for Your First Hunt</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>Keep the <a href="/quick-reference">Quick Reference</a> open</li>
								<li>Track Stamina carefully ‚Äî it's your lifeblood</li>
								<li>Coordinate Called Shots to break parts faster</li>
								<li>Don't be afraid to retreat if things go south</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 6: End of Hunt -->
					<section class="guide-section">
						<div class="section-number">6</div>
						<h2>End of Hunt</h2>

						<p><strong>If monster is defeated:</strong></p>

						<div class="end-hunt-flow">
							<div class="flow-step">
								<div class="flow-icon">üé≤</div>
								<h3>Roll on loot table</h3>
								<p>Determine what parts you can harvest</p>
							</div>

							<div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>

							<div class="flow-step">
								<div class="flow-icon">üî™</div>
								<h3>Harvest parts</h3>
								<p>Collect monster materials for crafting</p>
							</div>

							<div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>

							<div class="flow-step">
								<div class="flow-icon">üèòÔ∏è</div>
								<h3>Return to town</h3>
								<p>Rest and recover</p>
							</div>

							<div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>

							<div class="flow-step">
								<div class="flow-icon">‚öíÔ∏è</div>
								<h3>Craft gear</h3>
								<p>Use parts to build weapons and armor</p>
							</div>

							<div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>

							<div class="flow-step">
								<div class="flow-icon">üìà</div>
								<h3>Gain +1 Hunter Rank</h3>
								<p>(If Large hunt in your current tier)</p>
							</div>

							<div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>

							<div class="flow-step">
								<div class="flow-icon">‚ö°</div>
								<h3>Recover Stamina fully</h3>
								<p>Prepare for the next hunt</p>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="next-step-banner">
							<h3>Then prepare for the next tier.</h3>
							<p>As you gain Hunter Ranks, you'll unlock stronger monsters, better gear, and new abilities.</p>
							<p><strong>The hunt continues.</strong></p>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Quick Links -->
					<section class="quick-links">
						<h2>Ready to Hunt?</h2>
						<div class="link-grid">
							<a href="/character" class="link-card">
								<span class="link-icon">üë§</span>
								<h3>Character Creation</h3>
								<p>Full character building rules</p>
							</a>

							<a href="/quick-reference" class="link-card">
								<span class="link-icon">üìñ</span>
								<h3>Quick Reference</h3>
								<p>Combat rules at a glance</p>
							</a>

							<a href="/rules" class="link-card">
								<span class="link-icon">üìö</span>
								<h3>Core Rules</h3>
								<p>Deep dive into all systems</p>
							</a>

							<a href="/bestiary" class="link-card">
								<span class="link-icon">üêâ</span>
								<h3>Bestiary</h3>
								<p>Browse all monsters</p>
							</a>
						</div>
					</section>
				</article>
			</div>
		</main>

		<style>
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			:root {
				--forest-dark: #1a2e1a;
				--forest-green: #2d5016;
				--moss-green: #4a7c2f;
				--leaf-green: #6b9d3a;
				--amber: #d4a257;
				--earth-brown: #5c4033;
				--cream: #f5f1e8;
				--text-light: #e8e4d8;
				--danger-red: #c74440;
			}

			body {
				font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				color: var(--text-light);
				line-height: 1.7;
				min-height: 100vh;
			}

			.container {
				max-width: 1000px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 0 2rem;
			}

			/* Navigation */
			.nav {
				background: var(--forest-green);
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--amber);
				padding: 1rem 0;
				position: sticky;
				top: 0;
				z-index: 100;
			}

			.nav .container {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				max-width: 1200px;
			}

			.logo {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				font-weight: 900;
				color: var(--amber);
				text-decoration: none;
				letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
			}

			.nav-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 2rem;
			}

			.nav-links a {
				color: var(--cream);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
				transition: color 0.3s;
			}

			.nav-links a:hover {
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Breadcrumb */
			.breadcrumb {
				padding: 2rem 0 1rem;
			}

			.breadcrumb a {
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.breadcrumb a:hover {
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Page Header */
			.page-header {
				padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
				text-align: center;
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--amber);
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}

			.page-header h1 {
				font-size: 3rem;
				color: var(--amber);
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.subtitle {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				font-style: italic;
			}

			/* Content */
			.content {
				padding-bottom: 4rem;
			}

			/* Intro Banner */
			.intro-banner {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--moss-green) 0%, var(--forest-green) 100%);
				padding: 2rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 2px solid var(--amber);
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			/* Guide Sections */
			.guide-section {
				background: var(--forest-green);
				padding: 2.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				border: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
				position: relative;
			}

			.section-number {
				position: absolute;
				top: -20px;
				left: 2rem;
				width: 50px;
				height: 50px;
				background: var(--amber);
				color: var(--forest-dark);
				border-radius: 50%;
				font-size: 1.75rem;
				font-weight: 900;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				border: 3px solid var(--forest-dark);
			}

			.guide-section h2 {
				color: var(--amber);
				font-size: 2rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.section-subtitle {
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				font-style: italic;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.guide-section h3 {
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
			}

			.guide-section h4 {
				color: var(--amber);
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
			}

			.guide-section p {
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.guide-section ul {
				margin-left: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.guide-section li {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			/* Checklist Grid */
			.checklist-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				margin-top: 1.5rem;
			}

			.checklist-card {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.checklist-card.required {
				border-color: var(--amber);
			}

			.checklist-card.optional {
				border-color: var(--leaf-green);
			}

			.checklist-card h3 {
				color: var(--amber);
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
			}

			.checklist-card ul {
				list-style: none;
				margin: 0;
			}

			.checklist-card li {
				padding-left: 1.5rem;
				position: relative;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.checklist-card li:before {
				content: "‚ñ∏";
				position: absolute;
				left: 0;
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			.checklist-card a {
				color: var(--amber);
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			.checklist-card a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}

			/* Info Box */
			.info-box {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				border-left: 4px solid var(--leaf-green);
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.info-box p {
				margin: 0;
			}

			.info-box a {
				color: var(--amber);
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			.info-box a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}

			/* Step List */
			.step-list {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				margin-top: 1.5rem;
			}

			.step-card {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.step-header {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.step-num {
				background: var(--amber);
				color: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				font-weight: 700;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
			}

			.step-header h3 {
				color: var(--amber);
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 1.5rem;
			}

			.step-card p {
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
			}

			.step-card ul {
				margin-left: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
			}

			.step-card li {
				margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
			}

			/* Formula List */
			.formula-list {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0.75rem;
			}

			.formula {
				background: var(--moss-green);
				padding: 0.75rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				border-left: 4px solid var(--amber);
				font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--amber);
				text-align: center;
			}

			/* Role Grid */
			.role-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
				gap: 1rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0;
			}

			.role-card {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
				text-align: center;
			}

			.role-card h3 {
				color: var(--amber);
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
			}

			.role-card p {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.role-desc {
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				font-style: italic;
			}

			/* Callout Box */
			.callout-box {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				border-left: 4px solid var(--amber);
				margin-top: 1.5rem;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.callout-box p {
				margin: 0;
			}

			/* Hunt Checklist */
			.hunt-checklist {
				list-style: none;
				margin-left: 0;
			}

			.hunt-checklist li {
				padding-left: 1.5rem;
				position: relative;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.hunt-checklist li:before {
				content: "‚ñ∏";
				position: absolute;
				left: 0;
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Warning Banner */
			.warning-banner {
				background: rgba(199, 68, 64, 0.2);
				border: 2px solid var(--danger-red);
				padding: 1rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				margin: 1.5rem 0;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.warning-banner p {
				margin: 0;
			}

			/* Hunt Types */
			.hunt-types {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
				gap: 1rem;
				margin-top: 1.5rem;
			}

			.hunt-type-card {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 2px solid var(--leaf-green);
				text-align: center;
